334→                            <path d="M10 2a8 8 0 1 0 4.906 14.32l4.387 4.387a1 1 0 0 0 1.414-1.414L16.32 14.906A8 8 0 0 0 10 2Zm0 2a6 6 0 1 1 0 12a6 6 0 0 1 0-12Z"/>
335→                        </svg>
